                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.3.1">
                      <locus target="#125v" facs="130">Fol. 125v</locus>
                      <title>Notice of the end of the book of <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2362Songof">Song of Songs</ref></title>
                      <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተፈጸመ፡ መሐልየ፡ መሐልይ፡ ዘይሰመይ፡ ሰርደስሪን፡ ዝውእቱ፡ ስባሔ፡ ሰባሔያት፡ ሰጣዌ፡ ሰጣዌያት፡</incipit>
                      </msItem>
                      <note>Sample passage (<locus target="#120v" facs="125">fol. 120v</locus>): <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰርዲኖስ፡ ምስለ፡ ተርሴስ፡ ኢዮጶሎግዮስ፡ ዘምስለ፡ ሶፎር፡ ምስማኩ፡ ዘወርቅ። አቍላፊሁ፡ ወአቍፋሊሁ፡ ኢያሴምር።</foreign></note>
                </msItem>
